{"title":"听泉","authors":["石太瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"听泉\t〔苗族〕石太瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到家乡第一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走往山边去听泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听泉声呵望泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧恨新欢涌心田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往昔泉水不唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗家眼泪如流泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今人群泉边过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清泉水映彩衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜闻远处突突声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山下一座抽水站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水跳动万人乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇绿故乡一片天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着金色的早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响起隆隆的磨声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨声引人忆起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧日苦痛的情景："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜半起身推磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨声惨惨伴风吟："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞进去，一串泪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出来，一片哀声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代变新啊磨换新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今乐坏推磨人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞进去，一串笑语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出来，一堆黄金。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}